OL,3,CExtra #505 million for Wales in
OL,4,CChancellor's Autumn Budget
OL,6,FThere'll be an extra half a billion
OL,7,Fpounds for the Welsh Government to
OL,8,Fspend on services in Wales, following
OL,9,Fannouncements made in the UK Budget.
OL,11,FThe Chancellor said that there would
OL,12,Fbe an extra #505m added to the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment's budget between now and
OL,14,F2028 as a result of new spending
OL,15,Fcommitments in England.
