OL,3,CExtra #505 million for Wales in
OL,4,CChancellor's Autumn Budget
OL,6,FAnd as part of the budget, changes
OL,7,Fhave been announced to the way that
OL,8,FWales is funded which the UK
OL,9,FGovernment says will lead to #425m
OL,10,Fmore. It say it will also be fairer
OL,11,Fand give the Welsh Government more say
OL,12,Fover how it spends its money.
OL,14,FRachel Reeves said it proved that "two
OL,15,FLabour governments (were) working
OL,16,Ftogether in Wales to deliver for the
OL,17,Fpeople of Wales."
