OL,3,CExtra #505 million for Wales in
OL,4,CChancellor's Autumn Budget
OL,6,FOpposition politicians have repeatedly
OL,7,Faccused Labour at both ends of the M4
OL,8,Fof not recognising that Wales has
OL,9,Fdifferent needs to other parts of the
OL,10,FUK, because of its industrial heritage
OL,11,Fand an older, sicker population.
OL,13,FThere have long been calls, including
OL,14,Ffrom Labour, for the reform or
OL,15,Fabolition of the Barnett Formula,
OL,16,Fwhich is used to work out how much
OL,17,FWales gets as a share of funding
OL,18,Fearmarked for England.
