OL,3,CExtra #505 million for Wales in
OL,4,CChancellor's Autumn Budget
OL,6,FIn documents published alongside her
OL,7,Fbudget, the UK Government said that
OL,8,Fwhat's known as the 'fiscal framework
OL,9,Fwill be changed to ensure that Wales
OL,10,Fcan borrow more and access more of its
OL,11,Freserves.
OL,13,FCurrently it can only borrow #200m a
OL,14,Fyear and can only "draw down" #125m
OL,15,Ffor resource (day-to-day) spending and
OL,16,F#50m for capital (infrastructure)
OL,17,Fspending per year.
