OL,4,CChancellor's Autumn Budget
OL,6,FAs a result of the budget, those
OL,7,Famounts will increase by 10% and, for
OL,8,Fnext financial year only, the
OL,9,F"drawdown" cap will be lifted.
OL,11,FThe UK Government says the changes to
OL,12,Fthe fiscal framework will result in an
OL,13,Fextra #425m extra "spending power" for
OL,14,Fthe Welsh Government, in addition to
OL,15,Fthe extra #505m between now and 2028
OL,16,Fpassed on in this budget.
