OL,3,CExtra #505 million for Wales in
OL,4,CChancellor's Autumn Budget
OL,6,FThe Chancellor also announced that the
OL,7,Ftwo-child benefit cap would be lifted
OL,8,Fat an estimated cost of #3 billion by
OL,9,F2029-30 - something that a Labour
OL,10,Fsource described as "true Labour
OL,11,Fvalues in action."
OL,13,FThe source added that "In Wales it
OL,14,Fwill lift thousands of children out of
OL,15,Fpoverty and benefit thousands of
OL,16,Ffamilies many of whom are in work."
OL,18,FThe cap prevented parents from
OL,19,Fclaiming child tax credit or universal
OL,20,Fcredit for more than two children.
