OL,6,FShe told the Commons: "I have heard
OL,7,Frepresentations from Labour coalfield
OL,8,FMPs including my honourable friends
OL,9,Fthe members for Bassetlaw, Blyth and
OL,10,FAshington, Barnsley South, Mansfield
OL,11,Fand Llanelli. And today I can
OL,12,Fannounce, I will transfer the
OL,13,Finvestment reserve fund of the British
OL,14,Fcoal staff superannuation scheme to
OL,15,Fits members so that the men and the
OL,16,Fwomen who worked in our coal industry
OL,17,Fget a fair deal in their retirement
OL,18,Ftoo."
